Blood moon=
The [[blood moon armour]] set with the [[dual macuahuitl]] provides some of the highest damage-per-second and the best experience rates for melee. Using any other weapon, head, torso, or leg slot item will not allow usage of the set effect that increases your attack speed however, so they cannot be changed for gear with better or worse stats without losing a large portion of your DPS.
</br>
It will cost the most to upkeep however, at {{nocoins|100000}} gp/hr if repairing the armour with an NPC such as [[Bob]]. If fighting the boss for a very long time without needing to switch activities (and thus unequip the armour), it is possible to keep the set bonus from the armour even after it breaks, only losing a small amount of DPS from the lost strength bonus but incurring no further costs to use it.
