The atlatl is very potent for training Ranged if you have already trained [[Strength]] quite a bit past it, and can compete with rune knives or darts with much cheaper accompanying armour.

It is not important to aim for the full [[eclipse moon armour|eclipse moon armour set]] if other armour pieces allow you to deal more ranged damage-per-second, as the [[burn]] damage from the set bonus does not grant any extra [[experience]].

