High level=
While the [[Toxic blowpipe]] has the highest damage output of any weapon, it's also much more expensive to use for training. [[Void Knight equipment|Void ranged]] or [[Masori]] are both effective for training on the gemstone crab. Void will typically perform better, but Masori can be purchased right away from the [[Grand exchange]], without needing to be unlocked. Due to the crab’s low defences, the 2-tick attack speed of knives and darts allows for consistent hits, resulting in relatively high experience close to that of the blowpipe when paired with a high ranged strength off-hand like the [[twisted buckler]]. The low cost and competitive DPS of [[Rune knife|Rune knives]] and [[Rune dart|darts]] make them a very cost effective means of training. 

