Mid level=

[[Elder chaos robes]] provide a 3% magic damage bonus (1% per piece) and good accuracy, and require only 40 Magic and 1 Defence, making them a good low-mid level option for Magic. This magic damage is not enough on its own to grant a max hit, but with [[Mystic Lore]] active and casting [[Iban's Blast]], one can hit up to 26 damage. For those without access to [[Iban's staff]], a [[Smoke battlestaff]] in conjunction with the whole set and Mystic Lore can allow [[Fire Bolt]] to hit up to 17 damage.
</br>
[[Elite void knight equipment]] is a strong option, offering a 5% magic damage bonus alongside increased accuracy, enough for a max hit without using Prayer; however obtaining the set requires a significant time investment. It also requires completion of the hard [[Western Provinces Diary]], which requires 64 Magic; at which point [[Smoke Burst]] is available to players and can be used for much greater experience against monsters in [[multicombat]].
</br>
While the [[twinflame staff]] might appear to be an appealing option due to its higher damage output; the reduced attack speed, and no experience for the second spellcast means it provides less experience than other options.
